{"tid":2235204,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"理大圍城送檢DVD離奇分碎 電檢處2周後神回覆：光碟機整爛","createTime":"2020-10-08T13:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T04:48:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"0c129dd3839c2b662a208a60a4e4431e6ac24bc7","tid":2235204,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:05:32.000Z","msg":"獨立紀錄片電影《理大圍城》遭電影、 報刊及物品管理辦事處電影科（通稱電檢處）連番留難，包括要求在影片中加入警告字眼，但不得註明有關警告由電檢處要求，又在放映前2小時突被電檢處評為III級電影。另外，影意志送審的《理大圍城》DVD光碟離奇粉碎，但電檢處一直未有正式解釋事件，昨日（7日）電檢處終正式回覆影意志查詢，指光碟是在運行中的光碟機內破裂，而電影報刊辦亦已即時停用發生事故的光碟機。<br />\n<br />\n影意志今（８日）在Facebook專頁發文指，電檢處昨日終就《理大圍城》的事情正式回應影意志查詢，面對電影被評III級事宜、告示與影片內容不符等疑問，僅重複早前回應傳媒的查詢，並無詳細解釋清楚電影內容如何構成刑事罪行及誤導成份。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/3UWCFGNHSNBZVO5HNQB6FIVOYY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2F3UWCFGNHSNBZVO5HNQB6FIVOYY%2F&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=18d2c09a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2F3UWCFGNHSNBZVO5HNQB6FIVOYY%2F&h=d846b51a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/3UWCFGNHSNBZVO5HNQB6FIVOYY/</a>"},{"pid":"7550b42cd732f93b65f64cf095c68bd678f53fce","tid":2235204,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9a25f6e3e7b1a9c3e279eeda7268773dca18a3","tid":2235204,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" cla