/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T14:44:53.000Z","msg":"最多咪花晒, 我都想知佢部咩機可以攪碎隻碟, 定係佢機連碟一齊車落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c462ffb3c1f68b51fe36b185556709c21b857c24","tid":2235204,"uid":72994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:02:16.000Z","msg":"笑死人咩"},{"pid":"5684514fb995a88a6277d049c31f27e64045738a","tid":2235204,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c129dd3839c2b662a208a60a4e4431e6ac24bc7","tid":2235204,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T13:05:32.000Z","msg":"獨立紀錄片電影《理大圍城》遭電影、 報刊及物品管理辦事處電影科（通稱電檢處）連番留難，包括要求在影片中加入警告字眼，但不得註明有關警告由電檢處要求，又在放映前2小時突被電檢處評為III級電影。另外，影意志送審的《理大圍城》DVD光碟離奇粉碎，但電檢處一直未有正式解釋事件，昨日（7日）電檢處終正式回覆影意志查詢，指光碟是在運行中的光碟機內破裂，而電影報刊辦亦已即時停用發生事故的光碟機。<br />\n<br />\n影意志今（８日）在Facebook專頁發文指，電檢處昨日終就《理大圍城》的事情正式回應影意志查詢，面對電影被評III級事宜、告示與影片內容不符等疑問，僅重複早前回應傳媒的查詢，並無詳細解釋清楚電影內容如何構成刑事罪行及誤導成份。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/3UWCFGNHSNBZVO5HNQB6FIVOYY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2F3UWCFGNHSNBZVO5HNQB6FIVOYY%2F&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=18d2c09a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2F3UWCFGNHSNBZVO5HNQB6FIVOYY%2F&h=d846b51a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/3UWCFGNHSNBZVO5HNQB6FIVOYY/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:02:37.000Z","msg":"電檢處將被粉粹的先兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2f041cf7a73d55e50236bd1ba446cd001b9730","tid":2235204,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:07:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">【德國戰線聯署】絲打拍埋片教你點簽！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2231070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2231070</a><br />\n<br />\n德國政